## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

* Tile only support deployment for Splunk version 6.4 or above.
  For Splunk version 6.3 or below, please refer [this link](https://github.com/cloudfoundry-community/splunk-firehose-nozzle/tree/master#please-note) for deployment instructions.

